title: The Twenty-First Day | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The Twenty-First Day | Joel Osteen
description:
You may not see anything happening in the natural, but that doesn't mean God isn't working behind the scenes. Stay in faith. God not only heard your prayers; He has already set the miracle in motion. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
